Tailnets with more users allow you to experience richer use cases like file transfer, private web page and more. If they share your company email domain simply:

- Open the Users (https://info.tailscale.com/e3t/Ctc/OT+113/d4K34c04/VVxXMC6DMCBZW4J-nJ35ymMBGW1CR2895fYrZMN93kXHb3prCCW8wLKSR6lZ3phW8m9MM75VcJ0pVs8W-f6r8wCpW4jTy0c5pg7X7W8G-YkL7QGXCwW3-Qs7j6nbN7pW356G0V4VkjwwN4WPQzFv_3pZW7Wphr39cYsmVW7DnlXg5d0HxRW4H17Vj7yK-hfW1l7xsG7F_B1pW7NwhpH4LjyFNW1HcvTS1KY0t0W7rC1658bgP1FW2Lg5Z953fdg1W1WG8rB82fQFfW3vN_lq4D4SjFV6_GBn13y5pQW4Njncz5lW5CQW5YFq4N6Dv7NdVvG8kn7JJw88W1b_WM88ZqNSxW2Nz6LB2fz980W7ddzYR2K7sSdW4hBjMg4vy4tVN6XF5ZcLffVQW8hHMvM3rSNbkW1CySmX6cltZlf5_rFzd04 ) page of your admin console
- Click Invite users and select Invite via email
- Add any email addresses that use your company email domain.

